<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>نا عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٢٢٧ - عَنْ مَعْمَرٍ , عَنْ قَتَادَةَ , وَعِكْرِمَةَ ,<span class="c5"> فِي قَوْلِهِ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{مِنْ سِجِّيلٍ}</span> <span class="c4">[هود: ٨٢]</span> ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c1">" مِنْ طِينٍ <span class="c3">{مُسَوَّمَةً}</span> <span class="c4">[هود: ٨٣]</span> ,<span class="c5"> قَالَا:</span> "</span> مُطَوَّقَةٌ بِهَا نَضْحٌ مِنْ حُمْرَةٍ <span class="c3">{مَنْضُودٍ}</span> <span class="c4">[هود: ٨٢]</span> ,<span class="c5"> يَقُولُ:</span> <span class="c2">«مَصْفُوفَةٌ»</span> ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c3">{وَمَا هِيَ مِنَ الظَّالِمِينَ بِبَعِيدٍ}</span> <span class="c4">[هود: ٨٣]</span> ,<span class="c5"> يَقُولُ:</span> <span class="c2">«لَمْ يَبْرَأْ مِنْهَا ظَالِمٌ بَعْدَهُمْ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>